# 📋 Smart Attendance System

A smart, web-based attendance tracking system using **ESP32**, **MFRC522 RFID Reader**, **NTP (Network Time Protocol)**, and a real-time **web dashboard**. Designed to log attendance with RFID cards and display it dynamically with admin features.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 📶 **Wi-Fi Enabled ESP32** for real-time updates
- 🕒 **Real Date & Time** via NTP
- 📇 **RFID Authentication** using MFRC522
- 🌐 **Web Dashboard** with:
  - Live attendance table
  - Admin login page
  - CSV export for records
  - Date-based filtering
- 📟 Optional **LCD Display** for name and timestamp
- 🛡️ Secure admin access with login page

---

## 🧰 Hardware Used

| Component            | Description                     |
|---------------------|---------------------------------|
| ESP32               | Microcontroller with Wi-Fi      |
| MFRC522 RFID Module | For reading RFID tags/cards     |
| RC522 Tags          | RFID tags assigned to users     |
| LCD (I2C)           | Displays names and time (optional) |
| Buzzer (optional)   | For entry feedback sound        |
| Power Supply        | 5V USB or battery                |

---

## 🖥️ Web Interface

- **Login Page:** Secure access for admins  
- **Dashboard:**
  - Shows who is present
  - Real-time updates (auto-refresh every 2 seconds)
  - CSV export option
  - Date filter (view by day)

---

## 📦 File Structure

smart-attendance/
├── src/ # Arduino/ESP32 source code
├── data/ # HTML, CSS, JS files for web interface
